Description: Utilities to make ROS development easier
  ROS-Hacks provides useful aliases, functions, and keyboard shortcuts
  to enhance the ROS development experience. It includes workspace
  management, quick command execution, and various convenience
  functions for both ROS1 and ROS2 development.
